### Async Job Queue Integration - Test Requests
### Copy/paste these cURL commands or use in REST client (VS Code REST Client extension)

### Configuration
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@token = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

---

### 1. STRATEGY BACKTEST - Queue Job
POST {{baseUrl}}/strategies/strat123/backtest
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "timerange": "20230101-20231231",
  "pair": "BTC/USDT",
  "timeframe": "1h",
  "stakeAmount": 100
}

### Expected Response (202):
### {
###   "success": true,
###   "message": "Backtest queued",
###   "jobId": "strategy-backtest:abc-def-123",
###   "statusUrl": "/api/strategies/strat123/backtest-status/abc-def-123"
### }

---

