### 6. JOB STATUS - Get Full Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs/[REPLACE_WITH_JOB_ID]/status
Authorization: {{token}}

### Expected Response (200):
### {
###   "jobId": "strategy-backtest:abc-def-123",
###   "status": "processing",
###   "progress": 45,
###   "error": null,
###   "startedAt": "2026-03-03T10:00:00Z"
### }

---

### 7. JOB RESULT - Get Result (202 if processing)
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs/[REPLACE_WITH_JOB_ID]/result
Authorization: {{token}}

### Expected Response (202 while processing):
### {
###   "message": "Job still processing",
###   "status": "processing",
###   "progress": 45,
###   "jobId": "strategy-backtest:abc-def-123"
### }

### Expected Response (200 when completed):
### {
###   "jobId": "strategy-backtest:abc-def-123",
###   "result": { /* backtest results */ },
###   "completedAt": "2026-03-03T10:02:30Z"
### }

---

### 8. QUEUE STATS - Monitor Job Queue Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs/queue/strategy-backtest/stats
Authorization: {{token}}

### Expected Response (200):
### {
###   "queueType": "strategy-backtest",
###   "active": 1,
###   "waiting": 3,
###   "completed": 42,
###   "failed": 0
### }

---

### 9. RATE LIMITING TEST - Morio Chat (30/1min limit)
### Try 31 requests in rapid succession
### The 31st should return 429 Too Many Requests

POST {{baseUrl}}/morio/chat
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "daoId": "dao123",
  "message": "Test message"
}

### Expected after 30 successful requests:
### 429 Too Many Requests
### {
###   "error": "Rate limit exceeded"
### }

---

### 10. Check Different Queue Types
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs/queue/strategy-optimize/stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs/queue/morio-analyze/stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs/queue/morio-chat/stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs/queue/pool-rebalance/stats

