## Testing Workflow

### 1. Queue a job
POST /api/strategies/strat123/backtest → Save jobId

### 2. Poll status (10 times, 5 second intervals)
GET /api/jobs/{jobId}/status
Watch "progress" go from 10 → 90

### 3. Get result when complete
GET /api/jobs/{jobId}/result
Should return 200 with result object

### 4. Check queue health
GET /api/jobs/queue/strategy-backtest/stats
Should show: active: 0, completed: 1

### 5. Test rate limit
POST /api/morio/chat (31 times in 1 minute)
Should get 429 on 31st request

---

## Expected Performance Metrics

| Endpoint | Before | After | Status |
|----------|--------|-------|--------|
| POST backtest | 20-30s | 50ms | ✅ 400-600x faster |
| POST optimize | 60+s | 50ms | ✅ 1200+x faster |
| POST analyze | 10s | 50ms | ✅ 200x faster |
| POST chat | 5-10s | 50ms | ✅ 100-200x faster |
| POST rebalance | 5s | 50ms | ✅ 100x faster |

